snippet.title: Rise of the Slime - Announcement Trailer | PS5, PS4
snippet.description:
Be the hero that no-one saw coming in Rise of the Slime - a charming, relaxing and strategic deckbuilding adventure!

Coming this Summer to PS4 & PS5.
